{"tid":1153090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳打擊「三非」外國人　舉報市民可獲金錢獎勵","createTime":"2019-05-13T11:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T12:48:03.000Z","uid":224561,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"aa097eb66c42470e0bc2a879fc16f3d205d14c71","tid":1153090,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T11:55:47.000Z","msg":"深圳市公安局出入境管理局發布消息，為整頓市內的「三非」（即非法入境、非法居留、非法工作）外國人，或聘用相關外國人的單位及個人，舉報的市民將可獲得金錢獎勵。<br />\n<br />\n按規定，舉報屬公安機關尚未掌握且經公安機關查證屬實並予以處罰的，每行政拘留1人，獎勵500元（人民幣‧下同，約581港元）；每行政罰款1人，獎勵300元（約348港元）。<br />\n<br />\n市公安局公共信息網絡安全監察分局指，「三非」外國人在中國無合法身份，為生存而非法就業，勢必衝擊就業環境，且極易衍生系列犯罪問題，嚴重擾亂社會秩序穩定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190513/bkn-20190513174411587-0513_00952_001.html?refer=hn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190513%2Fbkn-20190513174411587-0513_00952_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHT3yU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=0cc0ac7b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190513/bkn-20190513174411587-0513_00952_001.html?refer=hn</a>"},{"pid":"6ee358fc6a7ab76097ccb05414953b08734dbd5e","tid":1153090,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T12:00:45.000Z","msg":"捉晒啲美國佬<br />\n唔畀佢地走資<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe6c16971994f017b411077b200ef7c1eaf9ef2","tid":1153090,"uid":4964,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T12:02:49.000Z","msg":"排外,心理不平衡,自以為高人一等,末落是必然的<br />\n又話來了就是深圳人?"},{"pid":"d35844568a5503d2828fb55b3c7119c80b00a490","tid":1153090,"uid":113626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T12:05:52.000Z","msg":"深圳大把非洲佬比你捉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89ce54703e93b3c61325709876d8c3327567312","tid":1153090,"uid":224561,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"